    <item>
      <title>泽西迈克 (Jersey Mike) 创始人在与黑石集团达成交易后身价升至 70 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/jersey-mike-s-founder-is-worth-7-billion-after-blackstone-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[1975 年，彼得·坎克罗做出了一个令大多数父母震惊的决定：放弃上大学的计划，背负巨额债务买下一家三明治店。半个世纪后，这个选择让他成为了亿万富翁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/jersey-mike-s-founder-is-worth-7-billion-after-blackstone-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 18:15:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pimco 业主的纽约大楼以低于其债务价值的价格出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/pimco-landlord-s-nyc-building-sells-for-less-than-value-of-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由太平洋投资管理公司 (Pacific Investment Management Co.) 业主支持的曼哈顿一栋办公楼的售价比其从黑石抵押贷款信托公司 (Blackstone Mortgage Trust Inc.) 借款的价值低约 6%，这难得一见地反映了纽约市房地产市场的压力状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/pimco-landlord-s-nyc-building-sells-for-less-than-value-of-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 17:20:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
